name: 甜花
text:
…………ほんとは……
がっかりしなきゃ……なんだよね……？

name: 甜花
text:
ダメそう、って……途中、思っちゃった……
けど……
trans:
In the middle... there... she thought that... she was a
failure......

name: 甜花
text:
……けど……甜花……
最後まで、諦めないで……
trans:
......But...... Tenka...... didn't give up... all the way to the
end......

name: 甜花
text:
甜花のこと……応援してくれる、人たち……
思い出して……
trans:
And she remembered...... all the people... that are
supporting her......

name: 甜花
text: 最後まで……ちゃんと、できた……
trans: She was able... to make it... to the end......

name: 甜花
text:
うん……
甜花……頑張れた……！
trans: Yeah...... Tenka... was able to work hard......!
